Lynda Mason Green is a Canadian actress. She played Dr. Suzanne McCullough in the television series War of the Worlds and Mrs. Quimby in the television series Ramona based on the books by Beverly Cleary. She had a bit role in Odyssey 5, in the episodes Rapture and Fossil. She portrayed Candace Scott, the daughter of a retired NASA astronaut. She also starred in PSI factor and Little Feathers {Information from FanCast} it is unknown if she is still acting. 
